  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libmediaart</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libmediaart</application> package contains a media
      art extraction and cache management library.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
